title: Rune Factory Frontier: Sora to Daichi no Boukenou
original_name: ルーンファクトリー フロンティア　空と大地の冒険王
sinopse:
An adventure fantasy starring Raguna and his feats as he arrives in Trampoli and discovers the mysterious "Whale" Island floating in the sky above it.
Mist and Iris also appear.
